Subject: [PATCH 1/4] feat: Brevo trust-signal overhaul + colorful premium
 theme

Trust & compliance fixes (Brevo reapplication):
- Remove all 3 fake testimonials from lib/data/site.js
- Replace testimonials section with TrustPillars (honest value-props)
- Fix inflated hero stats: '30+ Guides' -> '12 In-Depth Guides'
- Fix inflated portfolio GitHub stats: '500+ Stars/1,200+ Contributions' -> real, honest values
- Fix broken affiliate URL bug on /tools/brevo (AFFILIATE_URL was '#')
- Rewrite Brevo 'My Experience' with concrete SPF/DKIM/DMARC details
- Remove 'admin panel' note that suggested placeholder content

New legal pages (Brevo requires all 3):
- /privacy-policy (GDPR/CCPA compliant text)
- /terms (Terms of Service)
- /affiliate-disclosure (FTC-compliant)
- /about-author (real credentials, real bio, JSON-LD Person schema)

Footer overhaul:
- New Legal column linking all 4 new pages
- 'Published by Sumitkumar Pandit - real domain, real name, real GitHub' badge
- Email hello@codedbysumit.com everywhere (matches domain)

Colorful premium theme (retains light + dark):
- 6-color brand palette: emerald / purple / amber / cyan / pink / blue
- CSS vars for each brand color (light + dark tones)
- Rotating accent badges on cards (rainbow rotation)
- gradient-text, gradient-text-warm, gradient-text-cool utilities
- btn-primary-gradient, btn-warm-gradient, btn-cool-gradient
- icon-{emerald|purple|amber|cyan|pink|blue} for colorful icon tiles
- badge-{color} for tinted pill badges
- aurora-bg utility for hero/CTA glow layers
- glass-card-glow for gradient-border feature cards
- Colorful scrollbar, selection, rings
